Merge pull request #34 from jorispz/master

Move to React Router 1.0.0-beta2
Remove handleViewAction/handleServerAction in favor of simple dispatch()
Remove explicit RHL calls; if we even want to fix it it is really concern of RHL
Avoid empty screen on initial render
Update readme with correct code snippets
Eslint rule for space before fn parentheses
Utils fn should be exported singularly
Keep top-level functions declared as functions
Use ES7 class property for pure rendering components
Define propTypes as static class properties
Upgrade deps, enable ES7 exp ft. and lint
No need to setState when component did mount. Refs #23
Set default input value based on URL params
Explicitly enable strict mode for eslint
Use ES6 Object Literal Property Value Shorthand
Migrate Explore and get rid of LinkedStateMixin
Dirty migration of deprecated Navigation mixin

Merge pull request #22 from gaearon/higher-order-components

Use higher-order component instead of mixin and rewrite example in ES6
Explicitly opt into React Hot Loader for unexported components
Replace createStoreMixin with a higher-order component
Update webpack. NewWatchingPlugin is now default.
Use prefix to support usernames like `constructor`
Remove autofocus to avoid confusion when pressing Enter in location bar. Fixes #14.
Lock webpack version at 1.4.15 until webpack/webpack#703 is fixed
